                    "company": "VodafoneZiggo",
                    "description": "Responsible for all accounting activities for a diverse portfolio;\nMarketing - Making sure all Marketing related OPEX costs were correctly administered during the month but specifically during Month End Close. Mostly done through Purchase Orders.\nSales - Every Sales channel had their own process in terms of administration and accrual creation. My job was to make sure every channel (process) was up-to-date and accurate.\nZiggo Programming - Keeping track of all costs related to our Programming portfolio such as SVOD/TVOD services, Linear Television and Copyrights\nZiggo Sport - Keeping track of all P&L related activities of our Ziggo Sport portfolio such as Sport Rights costs, direct costs related to production and direct revenues.",
