                    "company": "VodafoneZiggo",
                    "description": "As Discover Trainee at VodafoneZiggo I am following an 18 month program consisting of three projects of each six months. Next to this, I get personal guidance from a dedicated Talent Manager for personal development and extensive training programs to broaden my skill set.\n\nFor my first project I am looking at process improvements for the CAPEX Accounting team within Financial Operations. I am responsible for multiple solutions concerning timely activation of assets through administrative adjustments, system integration and the facilitation of asset construction following Agile principles.\n\nFor my second project I got two assignments within the Technology business unit. Here I was asked to create a roadmap for provisioning tooling within the Technology B2B Services department, while also working on a financial network model for capacity planning within the IP & Transport department.\n\nFor my third, and final, trainee project I am asked to create performance management analyses for the different Real Estate asset classes present within the company. For this I will combine business, finance and Real Estate KPI's to set up a structural way of reporting different performance aspects.",
                    "title": "Discover Trainee Finance",
                    "employment_type": "Full-time"
                }
            ]
